        "explanation": "<div class=\"explanation-box\" style=\"text-align: left; padding: 15px; background: var(--bg-primary); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); margin-top: 10px; color: var(--text-primary);\">\n            <div style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--primary);\">📝 Detailed Explanation / 解説</div>\n            <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: var(--warning);\">English:</strong> The original meeting time was 2:00 ('二時の予定でした'). However, the man asks to change it to 3:00 ('三時からにしませんか') because his dentist visit ends at 2:30. The woman accepts, so they will meet at 3:00 ('三時に駅の前で会いましょう').\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5;\">\n                <strong style=\"color: var(--success);\">日本語:</strong> 元々は2時の約束でしたが、男性が「三時からにしませんか」と提案しました。2時半に歯医者が終わるためです。女性が「じゃあ、三時に」と承諾したため、二人は「三時」に会います。\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n                💡 <strong>Grammar Point:</strong> Time negotiation and scheduling\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary);\">\n                🏷️ <strong>Key Vocabulary:</strong> 約束, 歯医者, 駅の前\n            </div>\n        </div>",
